# Bayangol, Barguzinsky District, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Bayangol (; ) is a rural locality (an ulus) in Barguzinsky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 1,351 as of 2010. There are 16 streets.
Geography
Bayangol is located 65&nbsp;km northeast of Barguzin (the district's administrative centre) by road. Yubileyny is the nearest rural locality.
